10. Risks & Limitations
Risks
•	Customer ratings may be influenced by personal bias. 
•	High ratings do not necessarily indicate profitability. 
•	Customer engagement may be affected by factors not captured in the dataset. 
Limitations
•	The dataset does not contain revenue or profit information. 
•	Market conditions may have changed since the data was collected. 
•	Customer demographic information is unavailable. 
•	Some restaurants may be missing from the dataset. 
•	Results should be interpreted as market indicators rather than definitive business

